{"id": "16553", "revid": "43671602", "url": "https://divinity.fandom.com/wiki?curid=16553", "title": "Diseased (Status)", "text": "Diseased is a &lt;a href=\"Status%20Effects%20%28Original%20Sin%202%29\"&gt;status effect&lt;/a&gt; in \"\".\nDescription.\n is a negative status effect that lowers the victims &lt;a href=\"Constitution\"&gt;Constitution&lt;/a&gt; attribute by 2 points (thus lowering maximum Vitality points) as well as their damage output by 35 %. \nCause.\n status effect can be triggered three ways. First is by using certain skills/spells, second is by using grenades and third is by consuming uncooked food items such as uncooked meat, limbs and void-touched limbs and food. Lastly this status effect can be triggered by accepting kiss from &lt;a href=\"Radeka\"&gt;Radeka&lt;/a&gt;. \nTreatment.\nDiseased status effect can be treated by either negating the status effect or endured by keeping Physical armour above 0.\nStatus removal.\nAcid status effect is most efficiently removed by casting appropriate spells or using scrolls with said spells. "}
