{"id": "22518", "revid": "43671602", "url": "https://divinity.fandom.com/wiki?curid=22518", "title": "Divine Eye", "text": " is a &lt;a href=\"Divine%20Divinity%20skills\"&gt;Divine Skill&lt;/a&gt; in \"&lt;a href=\"Divine%20Divinity\"&gt;Divine Divinity&lt;/a&gt;\".\nDescription.\nA divine skill unlocked through &lt;a href=\"Begin%20the%20Blessing%20Ritual\"&gt;the Blessing Ritual&lt;/a&gt;. The Divine may summon and take control of a magical eye which will reveal all enemies in already explored (but not visible) areas. Enemies are neutral towards the eye and the eye cannot interact with them in any way. The skill can be cancelled during its duration by recasting it. Since it is a divine skill, it has no level requirement."}
