{"id": "18627", "revid": "31775388", "url": "https://divinity.fandom.com/wiki?curid=18627", "title": "Donalda", "text": " is a &lt;a href=\"Dwarves\"&gt;dwarf&lt;/a&gt; residing in &lt;a href=\"Arx\"&gt;Arx&lt;/a&gt; in 1242 AD.\nBackground.\nDonalda is a co-owner of the \"Genuine Dwarven Smithing and Ironmongering\" shop at Arx square near &lt;a href=\"Jemason\"&gt;Jemason&lt;/a&gt;'s shop. She is married to &lt;a href=\"Fionola\"&gt;Fionola&lt;/a&gt; and works as a blacksmith in their shop while her wife is trying to sell their goods."}
{"id": "12244", "revid": "43671602", "url": "https://divinity.fandom.com/wiki?curid=12244", "title": "Door to Eternity", "text": "Door to Eternity is an &lt;a href=\"Summoning%20%28Original%20Sin%202%29\"&gt;adept Summoning&lt;/a&gt; &lt;a href=\"Sourcery%20%28Original%20Sin%202%29\"&gt;source&lt;/a&gt; &lt;a href=\"Original%20Sin%202%20Skills\"&gt;skill&lt;/a&gt; in \"\".\nDescription.\nSkill.\nDoor to Eternity prevents all summoned creatures, in range and sight of the caster, to die from damage or disappear after their duration ends.\nSince relies on &lt;a href=\"Summoning\"&gt;Summoning&lt;/a&gt; magic it cannot be cast if caster is affected by &lt;a href=\"Silenced%20%28Status%29\"&gt;Silenced&lt;/a&gt; and &lt;a href=\"Enraged%20%28Status%29\"&gt;Enraged&lt;/a&gt; status effects.\nScroll and Skillbook.\n skillbook is a magical item that allows its reader to learn skill, if they have at least 3 points into &lt;a href=\"Original%20Sin%202%20Summoning\"&gt;Summoning&lt;/a&gt; &lt;a href=\"Attributes%20and%20Abilities%20%28Original%20Sin%202%29\"&gt;ability&lt;/a&gt;, and use it indefinitely. In order to be able to cast the skill, character needs 2 free memory slots. Note that the book will disappear once read. The book weights 0.5 and its base value is 800 gold. Since is a adept Summoning skill, traders will start selling the skillbook once &lt;a href=\"Godwoken\"&gt;Godwoken&lt;/a&gt; reach level 9.\n is one of the few magic-based skills in the game that does not have a scroll.\nLocations.\nTraders.\nFollowing table shows all NPCs who are guaranteed to sell summoning spellbooks, with their location and coordinates in the right column, from them. The location shown in the table (and the coordinates) are only for the initial location the NPC is in.\nAlso sold by &lt;a href=\"Hannag\"&gt;Hannag&lt;/a&gt; at &lt;a href=\"Cloisterwood\"&gt;Cloisterwood&lt;/a&gt;. However she only sells this spell alongside other Expert tier spells from other magic schools."}
