{"id": "3498", "revid": "27868532", "url": "https://divinity.fandom.com/wiki?curid=3498", "title": "Dragon Stone", "text": " is a type of &lt;a href=\"Divinity%20II%20quest%20items\"&gt;quest item&lt;/a&gt; in \"&lt;a href=\"Divinity%20II\"&gt;Divinity II&lt;/a&gt;\"\nCharacteristics.\nIt can be used to teleport to your &lt;a href=\"battle%20tower\"&gt;battle tower&lt;/a&gt;.\nLocations.\nAfter the main protagonist has successfully conquered the &lt;a href=\"Battle%20Tower\"&gt;Battle Tower&lt;/a&gt; on &lt;a href=\"Sentinel%20Island\"&gt;Sentinel Island&lt;/a&gt; from &lt;a href=\"Laiken\"&gt;Laiken&lt;/a&gt; with &lt;a href=\"Sassan\"&gt;Sassan&lt;/a&gt;'s help, he/she will receive a Dragon Stone along with a &lt;a href=\"Dragon%20Morph%20Stone\"&gt;Dragon Morph Stone&lt;/a&gt;."}
