{"id": "4537", "revid": "43671602", "url": "https://divinity.fandom.com/wiki?curid=4537", "title": "Dragon Wizard Bracers", "text": " are a &lt;a href=\"Dragon%20Knight%20Saga%20Armour%23Unique%20Armour%20List\"&gt;special bracers&lt;/a&gt; in \"\".\nDescription.\nDragon Wizard Bracers are special bracers that are part of the &lt;a href=\"Dragon%20Wizard%20Set\"&gt;Dragon Wizard Set&lt;/a&gt;. The whole set can be found across &lt;a href=\"Aleroth\"&gt;Aleroth&lt;/a&gt; and is consisted of &lt;a href=\"Dragon%20Wizard%20Helmet\"&gt;helmet&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a href=\"Dragon%20Wizard%20Cuirass\"&gt;cuirass&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a href=\"Dragon%20Wizard%20Bracers\"&gt;bracers&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a href=\"Dragon%20Wizard%20Leggings\"&gt;leggings&lt;/a&gt; and &lt;a href=\"Dragon%20Wizard%20Earrings\"&gt;earrings&lt;/a&gt;. It requires atleast level 35 in order to be worn. When worn the bracers will boost Magic Armour Rating by 7 points and &lt;a href=\"Spirit\"&gt;Spirit&lt;/a&gt; attribute by 9 points and &lt;a href=\"Vitality\"&gt;Vitality&lt;/a&gt; attribute by 5 points. Furthermore it will grant its wearer 5 points in &lt;a href=\"Firewall\"&gt;Firewall&lt;/a&gt; &lt;a href=\"Dragon%20Knight%20Saga%20Skills\"&gt;skill&lt;/a&gt;. The bracers have 1 charm slot and 2 enchantments slots. \nHow to Obtain.\nChest in the southwest corner of &lt;a href=\"Temple%20of%20Nimir%23Baldini%20Room\"&gt;the room&lt;/a&gt; where you pick \"&lt;a href=\"The%20Flower%20that%20doesn%27t%20Exist\"&gt;the flower that does not exist&lt;/a&gt;\" in the &lt;a href=\"Temple%20of%20Nimir\"&gt;Temple of Nimir&lt;/a&gt;. Press the button on the rear of a chest to make a platform appear that allows you to jump to the chest.\nSet Properties.\nDragon Wizard Bracers are a part of the Dragon Wizard Set which allows the item to gain additional, potentially increasing, properties the more items of the same set are worn. Dragon Wizard Bracers primary increased attribute is Indomitable Will, which is firstly gained by equipping 2 items from the set, and then increased by equipping more items from the set. "}
{"id": "4536", "revid": "43671602", "url": "https://divinity.fandom.com/wiki?curid=4536", "title": "Dragon Wizard Cuirass", "text": " is a &lt;a href=\"Dragon%20Knight%20Saga%20Armour%23Unique%20Armour%20List\"&gt;special cuirass&lt;/a&gt; in \"\". \nDescription.\nDragon Wizard Cuirass is a special cuirass that is part of the &lt;a href=\"Dragon%20Wizard%20Set\"&gt;Dragon Wizard Set&lt;/a&gt;. The whole set can be found across &lt;a href=\"Aleroth\"&gt;Aleroth&lt;/a&gt; and is consisted of &lt;a href=\"Dragon%20Wizard%20Helmet\"&gt;helmet&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a href=\"Dragon%20Wizard%20Cuirass\"&gt;cuirass&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a href=\"Dragon%20Wizard%20Bracers\"&gt;bracers&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a href=\"Dragon%20Wizard%20Leggings\"&gt;leggings&lt;/a&gt; and &lt;a href=\"Dragon%20Wizard%20Earrings\"&gt;earrings&lt;/a&gt;. It requires atleast level 35 in order to be worn. When worn the cuirass will boost Ranged Armour Rating by 7 points and &lt;a href=\"Spirit\"&gt;Spirit&lt;/a&gt; attribute by 9 points and &lt;a href=\"Vitality\"&gt;Vitality&lt;/a&gt; attribute by 14 points. Furthermore it will grant its wearer 5 points in &lt;a href=\"Way%20of%20the%20Battle%20Mage\"&gt;Way of the Battle Mage&lt;/a&gt; &lt;a href=\"Dragon%20Knight%20Saga%20Skills\"&gt;skill&lt;/a&gt;. The cuirass has 1 charm slot and 2 enchantments slots. \nHow to Obtain.\nGiven after mindreading &lt;a href=\"Nericon\"&gt;Nericon&lt;/a&gt;, an enchanted tree in &lt;a href=\"Mardaneus%20Plaza\"&gt;Mardaneus Plaza&lt;/a&gt;.\nSet Properties.\nDragon Wizard Cuirass is a part of the set Dragon Wizard Set which allows the item to gain additional, potentially increasing, properties the more items of the same set are worn. Dragon Wizard Cuirass primary increased attribute is Melee Armour Rating, which is firstly gained by equipping 2 items from the set, and then increased by equipping more items from the set. "}
{"id": "4539", "revid": "43671602", "url": "https://divinity.fandom.com/wiki?curid=4539", "title": "Dragon Wizard Earrings", "text": " are a &lt;a href=\"Dragon%20Knight%20Saga%20Accessories%23Earrings\"&gt;special earrings&lt;/a&gt; in \"\". \nDescription.\nDragon Wizard Earrings are a special earrings that are part of the &lt;a href=\"Dragon%20Wizard%20Set\"&gt;Dragon Wizard Set&lt;/a&gt;. The whole set can be found across &lt;a href=\"Aleroth\"&gt;Aleroth&lt;/a&gt; and is consisted of &lt;a href=\"Dragon%20Wizard%20Helmet\"&gt;helmet&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a href=\"Dragon%20Wizard%20Cuirass\"&gt;cuirass&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a href=\"Dragon%20Wizard%20Bracers\"&gt;bracers&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a href=\"Dragon%20Wizard%20Leggings\"&gt;leggings&lt;/a&gt; and &lt;a href=\"Dragon%20Wizard%20Earrings\"&gt;earrings&lt;/a&gt;. It requires atleast level 35 in order to be worn. When worn the earrings will boost &lt;a href=\"Strength\"&gt;Strength&lt;/a&gt; attribute by 5 points. Furthermore it will grant its wearer 5 points in &lt;a href=\"Destruction\"&gt;Destruction&lt;/a&gt; &lt;a href=\"Dragon%20Knight%20Saga%20Skills\"&gt;skill&lt;/a&gt;. The earrings have 1 charm slot and 2 enchantments slots. The default enchantments on the earrings are Damage Aura and Magic Damage Aura.\nHow to Obtain.\nThey are obtained by &lt;a href=\"mindread\"&gt;mindread&lt;/a&gt;ing the witch &lt;a href=\"Ursula\"&gt;Ursula&lt;/a&gt; at the &lt;a href=\"Prancing%20Seahorse%23Forbidden%20Archive\"&gt;Forbidden Archive&lt;/a&gt; in the &lt;a href=\"Prancing%20Seahorse\"&gt;Prancing Seahorse&lt;/a&gt; on &lt;a href=\"Lanilor%20Lane\"&gt;Lanilor Lane&lt;/a&gt;. If she is set free, they are automatically added to your inventory. If you choose to fight her, they can be looted from her remains afterwards.\nSet Properties.\nDragon Wizard Earrings are a part of the set Dragon Wizard Set which allows the item to gain additional, potentially increasing, properties the more items of the same set are worn. Dragon Wizard Earrings primary increased attribute is &lt;a href=\"Spirit\"&gt;Spirit&lt;/a&gt;, which is firstly gained by equipping 2 items from the set, and then increased by equipping more items from the set. "}
{"id": "4535", "revid": "43671602", "url": "https://divinity.fandom.com/wiki?curid=4535", "title": "Dragon Wizard Helmet", "text": " is a &lt;a href=\"Dragon%20Knight%20Saga%20Armour%23Unique%20Armour%20List\"&gt;special helmet&lt;/a&gt; in \"\". \nDescription.\nDragon Wizard Helmet is a special helmet that is part of the &lt;a href=\"Dragon%20Wizard%20Set\"&gt;Dragon Wizard Set&lt;/a&gt;. The whole set can be found across &lt;a href=\"Aleroth\"&gt;Aleroth&lt;/a&gt; and is consisted of &lt;a href=\"Dragon%20Wizard%20Helmet\"&gt;helmet&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a href=\"Dragon%20Wizard%20Cuirass\"&gt;cuirass&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a href=\"Dragon%20Wizard%20Bracers\"&gt;bracers&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a href=\"Dragon%20Wizard%20Leggings\"&gt;leggings&lt;/a&gt; and &lt;a href=\"Dragon%20Wizard%20Earrings\"&gt;earrings&lt;/a&gt;. It requires atleast level 35 in order to be worn. When worn the helmet will boost Melee Armour Rating by 6 points and &lt;a href=\"Intelligence\"&gt;Intelligence&lt;/a&gt; attribute by 5 points. Furthermore it will grant its wearer 5 points in &lt;a href=\"Mana%20Efficiency\"&gt;Mana Efficiency&lt;/a&gt; &lt;a href=\"Dragon%20Knight%20Saga%20Skills\"&gt;skill&lt;/a&gt;. The helmet has 3 charm slots and 2 enchantments slots. \nHow to Obtain.\nFound in a chest inside &lt;a href=\"Sir%20Gula%27s%20House\"&gt;Sir Gula's House&lt;/a&gt;. The chest can be opened after completing the quest &lt;a href=\"Fat%20Chance\"&gt;Fat Chance&lt;/a&gt;.\nSet Properties.\nDragon Wizard Helmet is a part of the set Dragon Wizard Set which allows the item to gain additional, potentially increasing, properties the more items of the same set are worn. Dragon Wizard Helmet primary increased attribute is &lt;a href=\"Intelligence\"&gt;Intelligence&lt;/a&gt;, which is firstly gained by equipping 2 items from the set, and then increased by equipping more items from the set. "}
