{"id": "17949", "revid": "49426621", "url": "https://divinity.fandom.com/wiki?curid=17949", "title": "Ducal Inn", "text": " is an Inn in &lt;a href=\"Verdistis\"&gt;Verdistis&lt;/a&gt;.\nLayout.\nBar.\nIn the bar area there is a fireplace to the north. Behind the counter are a couple of big casks of beer and wine barrels. Around the bar as well as in the storage area behind the counter are various beverages and food. The door from the storage to the street is locked (level 1), with the bronze key that opens it on the nearby table.\nInn.\nThe reception is to the east of the bar. There are six rooms in total, arranged around a cross-shaped hallway, only one of which is locked (level 2).\nCellar.\nThe cellar can be reached from the hatch next to &lt;a href=\"Rob\"&gt;Rob&lt;/a&gt;, but without membership of the &lt;a href=\"Thieves%20Guild\"&gt;Thieves Guild&lt;/a&gt; access is limited. In the first room down the hatch there are big casks of beer. The room to the east has a bar, where &lt;a href=\"Finnigan\"&gt;Finnigan&lt;/a&gt; is behind the counter. There are various beverages around the bar, as well as some wine barrels. Items such as beverages can be taken around Finnigan without him caring about it. The northern room is locked (level 1), and in that room are several more big casks of beer."}
