{"id": "12540", "revid": "53946974", "url": "https://divinity.fandom.com/wiki?curid=12540", "title": "Duggan", "text": "Duggan is a &lt;a href=\"dwarven\"&gt;dwarven&lt;/a&gt; &lt;a href=\"sourcerer\"&gt;sourcerer&lt;/a&gt; who resides at &lt;a href=\"Sanctuary%20of%20Amadia\"&gt;Sanctuary of Amadia&lt;/a&gt; in 1242 AD.\nBackground.\nDuggan is a sourcerer who was being shipped to &lt;a href=\"Fort%20Joy\"&gt;Fort Joy&lt;/a&gt; alongside sourcerer &lt;a href=\"Leya\"&gt;Leya&lt;/a&gt;. On their route to Fort Joy, through &lt;a href=\"Hollow%20Marshes\"&gt;Hollow Marshes&lt;/a&gt;, the magisters caravan transporting them was ambushed. Led by Gareth, the Seekers freed both Leya and Duggan and took them to their camp at &lt;a href=\"Sanctuary%20of%20Amadia\"&gt;Sanctuary of Amadia&lt;/a&gt;. There Duggan attempts to soothe &lt;a href=\"Leyla\"&gt;Leyla&lt;/a&gt; who is depressed after their leader &lt;a href=\"Gareth\"&gt;Gareth&lt;/a&gt; had not returned from his mission to retrieve soulforged weapons that would help them defeat the Shriekers.\nDuggan may join the group during Call to Arms and can be located at the Abandoned Camp afterward. Additionally, Duggan may be encountered on the Lady Vengeance before reaching Reaper's Coast. Unfortunately, Duggan goes missing in action after the party arrives at Reaper's Coast."}
