{"id": "19589", "revid": "49426621", "url": "https://divinity.fandom.com/wiki?curid=19589", "title": "Ruganol", "text": " is a character mentioned only in \"&lt;a href=\"Divine%20Divinity\"&gt;Divine Divinity&lt;/a&gt;\" and known as the \"First Healer\" in &lt;a href=\"Rivellon\"&gt;Rivellon&lt;/a&gt;. He rediscovered &lt;a href=\"Source\"&gt;Source&lt;/a&gt; in the &lt;a href=\"Age%20of%20Deception\"&gt;Age of Deception&lt;/a&gt; and sought to return this knowledge to the world.\nBackground.\nAn old man and meditation-healer from beyond the known reaches of Rivellon, Ruganol brought the knowledge of &lt;a href=\"Source\"&gt;Source&lt;/a&gt; back to the region during the &lt;a href=\"Age%20of%20the%20Damned\"&gt;Age of the Damned&lt;/a&gt; circa &lt;a href=\"Timeline\"&gt;600 AD&lt;/a&gt;. After the &lt;a href=\"Demons\"&gt;demon&lt;/a&gt; armies had laid siege to &lt;a href=\"Rivertown\"&gt;Rivertown&lt;/a&gt;, he offered his services to the then duke, &lt;a href=\"Dylan%20Ferol\"&gt;Dylan Ferol&lt;/a&gt;. His assistance was accepted by Dylan, and Ruganol took to teaching the healers of the region how to use Source in their work. This knowledge helped turn the tide of the war. Rugonal then took to new lands in order to further the spread of his knowledge."}
