{"id": "15714", "revid": "31775388", "url": "https://divinity.fandom.com/wiki?curid=15714", "title": "Sanguinia Tell", "text": "Sanguinia Tell is a &lt;a href=\"demon\"&gt;demon&lt;/a&gt; residing in &lt;a href=\"Arx\"&gt;Arx&lt;/a&gt; in 1242 AD.\nBackground.\nSanguinia Tell is a demon in a guise of an old human woman who resides in school district of Arx. \nShe makes her living by lending money but she is capable of trading rings and belts as well. Anyone is free to ask her for money, however she demands a deposit in form of the borrower's blood. If the borrower cannot pay the money owed plus 50% interest then the borrower dies.\nInterestingly Sanguinia had lended money to &lt;a href=\"Beryl%20Griff\"&gt;Beryl Griff&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a href=\"Lovrik\"&gt;Lovrik&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a href=\"Dorotya\"&gt;Dorotya&lt;/a&gt; and &lt;a href=\"Garvan\"&gt;Garvan&lt;/a&gt;. Their blood vials can be found in her cellar."}
