{"id": "4544", "revid": "43671602", "url": "https://divinity.fandom.com/wiki?curid=4544", "title": "Shadow Archer Bracers", "text": " are a &lt;a href=\"Dragon%20Knight%20Saga%20Armour%23Unique%20Armour%20List\"&gt;special bracers&lt;/a&gt; in \"\".\nDescription.\nShadow Archer Cuirass is a special cuirass that is part of the &lt;a href=\"Shadow%20Archer%20Set\"&gt;Shadow Archer Set&lt;/a&gt;. The whole set can be found across &lt;a href=\"Aleroth\"&gt;Aleroth&lt;/a&gt; and is consisted of &lt;a href=\"Shadow%20Archer%20Helmet\"&gt;helmet&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a href=\"Shadow%20Archer%20Cuirass\"&gt;cuirass&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a href=\"Shadow%20Archer%20Bracers\"&gt;bracers&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a href=\"Shadow%20Archer%20Leggings\"&gt;leggings&lt;/a&gt; and &lt;a href=\"Shadow%20Archer%20Bracelet\"&gt;bracelet&lt;/a&gt;. It requires atleast level 35 in order to be worn. When worn the bracers will boost Melee Armour Rating by 5 points and &lt;a href=\"Spirit\"&gt;Spirit&lt;/a&gt; attribute by 7 points. Furthermore it will grant its wearer 5 points in &lt;a href=\"Ranger%20Strength\"&gt;Ranger Strength&lt;/a&gt; &lt;a href=\"Dragon%20Knight%20Saga%20Skills\"&gt;skill&lt;/a&gt;. The bracers have 1 charm slot and 2 enchantments slots. \nHow to Obtain.\nCan be found in a chest inside the basement of the &lt;a href=\"Healers%27%20House\"&gt;Healers' House&lt;/a&gt;. &lt;a href=\"Mindread\"&gt;Mindread&lt;/a&gt; &lt;a href=\"Decimus\"&gt;Decimus&lt;/a&gt; &amp; ask &lt;a href=\"Bernard\"&gt;Bernard&lt;/a&gt; for the basement chest key at the Healers' House. \nSet Properties.\nShadow Archer Bracers is a part of the set Shadow Archer Set which allows the item to gain additional, potentially increasing, properties the more items of the same set are worn. Shadow Archer Bracers primary increased attribute is &lt;a href=\"Dexterity\"&gt;Dexterity&lt;/a&gt;, which is firstly gained by equipping 2 items from the set, and then increased by equipping more items from the set. "}
{"id": "4543", "revid": "43671602", "url": "https://divinity.fandom.com/wiki?curid=4543", "title": "Shadow Archer Cuirass", "text": " is a &lt;a href=\"Dragon%20Knight%20Saga%20Armour%23Unique%20Armour%20List\"&gt;special cuirass&lt;/a&gt; in \"\". \nDescription.\nShadow Archer Cuirass is a special cuirass that is part of the &lt;a href=\"Shadow%20Archer%20Set\"&gt;Shadow Archer Set&lt;/a&gt;. The whole set can be found across &lt;a href=\"Aleroth\"&gt;Aleroth&lt;/a&gt; and is consisted of &lt;a href=\"Shadow%20Archer%20Helmet\"&gt;helmet&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a href=\"Shadow%20Archer%20Cuirass\"&gt;cuirass&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a href=\"Shadow%20Archer%20Bracers\"&gt;bracers&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a href=\"Shadow%20Archer%20Leggings\"&gt;leggings&lt;/a&gt; and &lt;a href=\"Shadow%20Archer%20Bracelet\"&gt;bracelet&lt;/a&gt;. It requires atleast level 35 in order to be worn. When worn the cuirass will boost &lt;a href=\"Spirit\"&gt;Spirit&lt;/a&gt; and &lt;a href=\"Vitality\"&gt;Vitality&lt;/a&gt; by 9 points each and Magic Armour Rating by 5 points. Furthermore it will grant its wearer 5 points in &lt;a href=\"Way%20of%20the%20Ranger\"&gt;Way of the Ranger&lt;/a&gt; &lt;a href=\"Dragon%20Knight%20Saga%20Skills\"&gt;skill&lt;/a&gt;. The cuirass has 1 charm slot and 2 enchantments slots. The default enchantments are Magic Damage Aura and Retribution Aura.\nHow to Obtain.\nCan be bought from &lt;a href=\"Brancussi\"&gt;Brancussi&lt;/a&gt; dispatched to &lt;a href=\"Willy%27s%20House\"&gt;Willy's House&lt;/a&gt;, or simply by killing him.\nSet Properties.\nShadow Archer Cuirass are a part of the Shadow Archer Set which allows the item to gain additional, potentially increasing, properties the more items of the same set are worn. Shadow Archer Cuirass primary increased attribute is Conditioned Body, which is firstly gained by equipping 2 items from the set, and then increased by equipping more items from the set. "}
