{"id": "2231", "revid": "43671602", "url": "https://divinity.fandom.com/wiki?curid=2231", "title": "Skill Training Arena", "text": "The Skill Training Arena, is an area of your &lt;a href=\"Battle%20Tower\"&gt;Battle Tower&lt;/a&gt; where your &lt;a href=\"Skill%20Trainer\"&gt;Skill Trainer&lt;/a&gt; resides in \"\". Your skill trainer can teach you skills past your learning potential. Depending on who you pick for your skill trainer, the skills that you will be able to learn change. Some skills cannot be learned past level 5."}
