{"id": "11581", "revid": "43671602", "url": "https://divinity.fandom.com/wiki?curid=11581", "title": "Skin Graft", "text": "Skin Graft is an &lt;a href=\"Polymorph%20%28Skill%20Class%29\"&gt;adept Polymorph&lt;/a&gt; &lt;a href=\"Sourcery%20%28Original%20Sin%202%29\"&gt;source&lt;/a&gt; &lt;a href=\"Original%20Sin%202%20Skills\"&gt;skill&lt;/a&gt; in \"\".\nDescription.\nSkill.\nSkin graft resets your abilities allowing you to reuse them immediately. Removes &lt;a href=\"Burning%20%28Status%29\"&gt;Burning&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a href=\"Necrofire%20%28Status%29\"&gt;Necrofire&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a href=\"Poisoned%20%28Status%29\"&gt;Poisoned&lt;/a&gt; and &lt;a href=\"Bleeding%20%28Status%29\"&gt;Bleeding&lt;/a&gt;. Physical and Magic armor are set to zero. \nSince relies on &lt;a href=\"Metamorphosis\"&gt;Metamorphosis&lt;/a&gt; magic it cannot be cast if caster is affected by &lt;a href=\"Silenced%20%28Status%29\"&gt;Silenced&lt;/a&gt; and &lt;a href=\"Enraged%20%28Status%29\"&gt;Enraged&lt;/a&gt; status effects.\nScroll and Skillbook.\n skillbook is a magical item that allows its reader to learn skill, if they have at least 3 points into &lt;a href=\"Original%20Sin%202%20Polymorph\"&gt;Polymorph&lt;/a&gt; &lt;a href=\"Attributes%20and%20Abilities%20%28Original%20Sin%202%29\"&gt;ability&lt;/a&gt;, and use it indefinitely. In order to be able to cast the skill, character needs 2 free memory slots. Note that the book will disappear once read. The book weights 0.5 and its base value is 800 gold. A skillbook can be crafted if a scroll is combined with a &lt;a href=\"Blank%20Polymorph%20Skillbook\"&gt;Blank Polymorph Skillbook&lt;/a&gt;. Since is an adept Polymorph skill, traders will start selling the skillbook once &lt;a href=\"Godwoken\"&gt;Godwoken&lt;/a&gt; reach level 9.\n scroll is a magical item that allows any character to cast skill, regardless of skill prerequisites, but in the case of skill only once per combat. The scroll is craftable, weights 0.02 and has base value of 100 gold.\nLocations.\nTraders.\nFollowing table shows all NPCs who are guaranteed to sell Polymorph spellbooks, with their location and coordinates in the right column, from them. The location shown in the table (and the coordinates) are only for the initial location the NPC is in. Note that some of these may have other spell/skillbooks and goods to sell. "}
