{"id": "2478", "revid": "43671602", "url": "https://divinity.fandom.com/wiki?curid=2478", "title": "Breaking an Entry", "text": " is a &lt;a href=\"Ego%20Draconis%20quests\"&gt;main quest&lt;/a&gt; given by &lt;a href=\"Sassan\"&gt;Sassan&lt;/a&gt; in \"\". "}
{"id": "12265", "revid": "43671602", "url": "https://divinity.fandom.com/wiki?curid=12265", "title": "Breathing Bubble", "text": "Breathing Bubble is a &lt;a href=\"Aerotheurge%20%28Original%20Sin%202%29\"&gt;Aerotheurge&lt;/a&gt; and &lt;a href=\"Warfare%20%28Original%20Sin%202%29\"&gt;Warfare&lt;/a&gt; skill in \"\".\nDescription.\nSkill.\n is a supportive mixed skill that allows caster to create a bubble of clean air around their head. This bubble of air will protect the caster for 5 turns from all cloud surfaces (including their blessed variants and Deathfog) as well as grant immunity to: &lt;a href=\"Suffocating%20%28Status%29\"&gt;Suffocating&lt;/a&gt; and &lt;a href=\"Silenced%20%28Status%29\"&gt;Silenced&lt;/a&gt; status effects. Since caster will become immune to &lt;a href=\"Enraged%20%28Status%29\"&gt;Enraged&lt;/a&gt; status effect as well they will be immune to the &lt;a href=\"Original%20Sin%202%20Warfare\"&gt;Warfare&lt;/a&gt; skill &lt;a href=\"Enrage\"&gt;Enrage&lt;/a&gt;.\nSince relies on &lt;a href=\"Aerotheurgy\"&gt;Aerotheurgy&lt;/a&gt; magic it cannot be cast if caster is affected by &lt;a href=\"Silenced%20%28Status%29\"&gt;Silenced&lt;/a&gt; and &lt;a href=\"Enraged%20%28Status%29\"&gt;Enraged&lt;/a&gt; status effects.\nScroll and Skillbook.\n skillbook is a magical item that allows its reader to learn skill, if they have at least 1 point into both &lt;a href=\"Original%20Sin%202%20Aerotheurge\"&gt;Aerotheurge&lt;/a&gt; and &lt;a href=\"Original%20Sin%202%20Warfare\"&gt;Warfare&lt;/a&gt; &lt;a href=\"Attributes%20and%20Abilities%20%28Original%20Sin%202%29\"&gt;abilities&lt;/a&gt;, and use it indefinitely. In order to be able to cast the skill, character needs 1 free memory slot. Note that the book will disappear once read. The book weights 0.5 and its base value is 190 gold. A skillbook can be crafted if a any non-source &lt;a href=\"Original%20Sin%202%20Aerotheurge\"&gt;Aerotheurge&lt;/a&gt; and &lt;a href=\"Original%20Sin%202%20Warfare\"&gt;Warfare&lt;/a&gt; skillbooks are combined. Since is a mixed skill, traders do not have the skillbook for sale.\n is one of the few magic-based skills in the game that does not have a scroll.\nSkill Modifiers.\n is a supportive aerotheurge skill that provides set bonuses and as such it is not affected by the Level, Aerotheurge ability and &lt;a href=\"Intelligence\"&gt;Intelligence&lt;/a&gt; attribute of the caster.\nHowever the skill itself can still be affected by other skills.\nLocation.\nTraders.\nThis skill cannot be bought or stolen from NPCs."}
