{"id": "16642", "revid": "31775388", "url": "https://divinity.fandom.com/wiki?curid=16642", "title": "Candor", "text": " was a &lt;a href=\"Godwoken\"&gt;Godwoken&lt;/a&gt; student at &lt;a href=\"the%20Academy%20of%20the%20Seven\"&gt;the Academy of the Seven&lt;/a&gt; on &lt;a href=\"the%20Nameless%20Isle\"&gt;the Nameless Isle&lt;/a&gt;.\nBackground.\nCandor is an &lt;a href=\"Elves\"&gt;elven&lt;/a&gt; Godwoken student who studied at the Ancient Academy. At some point in time he thought he was ready to step up should &lt;a href=\"Lucian\"&gt;Lucian&lt;/a&gt; lose the war, even though his tutors disagreed and did not allow him to fight in &lt;a href=\"the%20Arena%20of%20the%20One\"&gt;the Arena of the One&lt;/a&gt;. \nDetermined he went to see the &lt;a href=\"Chancellor\"&gt;Chancellor&lt;/a&gt; to hear his case. In his office though he met a great and a powerful &lt;a href=\"Sourcerer\"&gt;Sourcerer&lt;/a&gt; he never met. When the man came closer he realised it was Lucian. As Lucian gave him \"a smile of the utmost benevolence and grace\" Candor realised he was far from ready. Candor fled towards the library to warn his tutors but Lucian, who was way faster, cuts him down. \nEven in death though, he still believes he will be the next Divine."}
{"id": "12237", "revid": "43671602", "url": "https://divinity.fandom.com/wiki?curid=12237", "title": "Cannibalize", "text": "Cannibalize is a &lt;a href=\"Original%20Sin%202%20Summoning\"&gt;master Summoning&lt;/a&gt; &lt;a href=\"Original%20Sin%202%20Skills\"&gt;skill&lt;/a&gt; in \"\".\nDescription.\nSkill.\nCannibalize destroys an allied summon or totem. Caster receives up to 100% of their Vitality, Physical Armour and Magic Armour.\nSince relies on &lt;a href=\"Summoning\"&gt;Summoning&lt;/a&gt; magic it cannot be cast if caster is affected by &lt;a href=\"Silenced%20%28Status%29\"&gt;Silenced&lt;/a&gt; and &lt;a href=\"Enraged%20%28Status%29\"&gt;Enraged&lt;/a&gt; status effects.\nScroll and Skillbook.\n skillbook is a magical item that allows its reader to learn skill, if they have at least 3 points into &lt;a href=\"Original%20Sin%202%20Summoning\"&gt;Summoning&lt;/a&gt; &lt;a href=\"Attributes%20and%20Abilities%20%28Original%20Sin%202%29\"&gt;ability&lt;/a&gt;, and use it indefinitely. In order to be able to cast the skill, character needs 1 free memory slot. Note that the book will disappear once read. The book weights 0.5 and its base value is 1400 gold. Since is a master Summoning skill, traders will start selling the skillbook once &lt;a href=\"Godwoken\"&gt;Godwoken&lt;/a&gt; reach level 16.\n is one of the few magic-based skills in the game that does not have a scroll.\nLocations.\nTraders.\nFollowing table shows all NPCs who are guaranteed to sell summoning spellbooks, with their location and coordinates in the right column, from them. The location shown in the table (and the coordinates) are only for the initial location the NPC is in."}
