{"id": "13479", "revid": "49426621", "url": "https://divinity.fandom.com/wiki?curid=13479", "title": "Catch the Thief!", "text": " is a &lt;a href=\"Divine%20Divinity%20quests\"&gt;quest&lt;/a&gt; in \"&lt;a href=\"Divine%20Divinity\"&gt;Divine Divinity&lt;/a&gt;\".\nDetailed walkthrough.\nWhen traveling in Farmlands, &lt;a href=\"Lucian\"&gt;Lucian&lt;/a&gt; encounters Tom, who has lost many of his cattle due thievery. He knows the thief must be nearby since it is impossible to lead stolen cows more than few miles without drawing attention in the area. The cattle, or what iss left of them, can be found in &lt;a href=\"poor%20area\"&gt;poor area&lt;/a&gt;, in Dorian's cellar.\nUpon confronting Dorian about the meat in his cellar, he admits being the thief, since it was only way for him to survive. Either turn Dorian in, rewarding some experience and a +2 reputation increase with Tom and a reputation decrease of -10 with Dorian, as well as him being executed due to thievery, or keep Dorian's secret, which rewards less experience, but increases one's reputation Tom by 3, and Dorian's by 28. However, upon returning to Tom (not necessary), he says that town inspector found out thief being Dorian, who is now in jail."}
