{"id": "12220", "revid": "43671602", "url": "https://divinity.fandom.com/wiki?curid=12220", "title": "Challenge", "text": "Challenge is a &lt;a href=\"warfare%20%28Original%20Sin%202%29\"&gt;master Warfare&lt;/a&gt; &lt;a href=\"Original%20Sin%202%20Skills\"&gt;skill&lt;/a&gt; in \"\".\nDescription.\nSkill.\nMark enemy target. If they die in the next 2 turns, you are healed and receive damage and armor bonuses. If target survives, their Vitality is restored to full and the caster takes damage.\nScroll and Skillbook.\n skillbook is a magical item that allows its reader to learn skill, if they have at least 3 points into &lt;a href=\"Original%20Sin%202%20Warfare\"&gt;Warfare&lt;/a&gt; &lt;a href=\"Attributes%20and%20Abilities%20%28Original%20Sin%202%29\"&gt;ability&lt;/a&gt;, and use it indefinitely. In order to be able to cast the skill, character needs 1 free memory slot. Note that the book will disappear once read. The book weights 0.5 and its base value is 1400 gold. Since is a master Warfare skill, traders will start selling the skillbook once player character or their &lt;a href=\"Original%20Sin%202%20Companions\"&gt;companions&lt;/a&gt; reach level 16.\nSince is a weapon based skill and as such it does not have a scroll. It is also not possible to craft a skillbook.\nLocations.\nTraders.\nFollowing table shows all NPCs who are guaranteed to sell warfare skillbooks, with their location and coordinates in the right column, from them. The location shown in the table (and the coordinates) are only for the initial location the NPC is in. Note that some of these may have other spell/skillbooks and goods to sell. &lt;a href=\"Gareth\"&gt;Gareth&lt;/a&gt; may follow the Godwoken on &lt;a href=\"The%20Lady%20Vengeance\"&gt;Lady Vengeance&lt;/a&gt; if his demands are met."}
{"id": "3810", "revid": "31775388", "url": "https://divinity.fandom.com/wiki?curid=3810", "title": "Chambers of Blood", "text": " is a &lt;a href=\"Books%20and%20notes%20%28Dragon%20Knight%20Saga%29%23Flames%20of%20Vengeanace\"&gt;script&lt;/a&gt; in \"\".\nBackground.\nChambers of Blood is an ancient, anonymous play that remains popular due to its controversial theme and content.\nIt involves a group of women who form a secret cabal of sorceresses that wants to invoke the spirit of the &lt;a href=\"demon\"&gt;demon&lt;/a&gt; Astaroth, so that they can bare him demonspawn that will bring them power and riches.\nIn the words of &lt;a href=\"Alfred\"&gt;Alfred&lt;/a&gt;: "}
{"id": "11509", "revid": "43671602", "url": "https://divinity.fandom.com/wiki?curid=11509", "title": "Chameleon Cloak", "text": " is a &lt;a href=\"Polymorph%20%28Skill%20Class%29\"&gt;starter Polymorph&lt;/a&gt; &lt;a href=\"Original%20Sin%202%20Skills\"&gt;skill&lt;/a&gt; in \"\".\nDescription.\nSkill.\n is a supportive polymorph skill that allows caster to transform their body. skill causes caster to become &lt;a href=\"Invisible%20%28Status%29\"&gt;Invisible&lt;/a&gt; for 2 turns or until they attack, receive damage or receive a status effect such as &lt;a href=\"Wet%20%28Status%29\"&gt;Wet&lt;/a&gt;. Unlike most skills the can be cast if caster is already Invisible or Sneaking without breaking them. \nSince relies on &lt;a href=\"Metamorphosis\"&gt;Metamorphosis&lt;/a&gt; magic it cannot be cast if caster is affected by &lt;a href=\"Silenced%20%28Status%29\"&gt;Silenced&lt;/a&gt; and &lt;a href=\"Enraged%20%28Status%29\"&gt;Enraged&lt;/a&gt; status effects. \nScroll and Skillbook.\n skillbook is a magical item that allows its reader to learn skill, if they have at least 1 point into &lt;a href=\"Original%20Sin%202%20Polymorph\"&gt;Polymorph&lt;/a&gt; &lt;a href=\"Attributes%20and%20Abilities%20%28Original%20Sin%202%29\"&gt;ability&lt;/a&gt;, and use it indefinitely. In order to be able to cast the skill, character needs 1 free memory slot. Note that the book will disappear once read. The book weights 0.5 and its base value is 120 gold. A skillbook can be crafted if a scroll is combined with a &lt;a href=\"Blank%20Polymorph%20Skillbook\"&gt;Blank Polymorph Skillbook&lt;/a&gt;. Since is a starter Polymorph skill, it is available right from the start of the game. Traders selling Polymorph skillbooks will have this book for sale since the start of the game as well. \n scroll is a magical item that allows any character to cast skill, regardless of skill prerequisites, but only once. The only limiting element in casting this way is the amount of &lt;a href=\"Original%20Sin%202%20Action%20Points\"&gt;Action Points (AP)&lt;/a&gt; character has at their disposal in current turn. The scroll is craftable, weights 0.02 and has base value of 100 gold.\nThe cost of Action Points between scroll and skill themselves remains the same. Both the scroll and the skill itself are affected by other skills, attributes and talents that may provide additional bonuses.\nSkill Modifiers.\n is a supportive skill that provides a positive status effect for its caster. As such the bonus itself or the range of the skill cannot be increased. However this skill is affected by other skills such as &lt;a href=\"Time%20Warp\"&gt;Time Warp&lt;/a&gt; or &lt;a href=\"Skin%20Graft\"&gt;Skin Graft&lt;/a&gt;.\nLocations.\nTraders.\nFollowing table shows all NPCs who are guaranteed to sell Polymorph spellbooks, with their location and coordinates in the right column, from them. The location shown in the table (and the coordinates) are only for the initial location the NPC is in. Note that some of these may have other spell/skillbooks and goods to sell. "}
