{"id": "2096", "revid": "43671602", "url": "https://divinity.fandom.com/wiki?curid=2096", "title": "Chasing the Dragon", "text": " is a &lt;a href=\"Ego%20Draconis%20quests\"&gt;main quest&lt;/a&gt; given by &lt;a href=\"Rhode\"&gt;Rhode&lt;/a&gt; in \"\".\nDetailed Walkthrough.\n is a main quest automatically accepted upon entering &lt;a href=\"Broken%20Valley\"&gt;Broken Valley&lt;/a&gt;. Commander &lt;a href=\"Rhode\"&gt;Rhode&lt;/a&gt; will tell you to find as much information as possible from residents of &lt;a href=\"Broken%20Valley%20Village\"&gt;Broken Valley Village&lt;/a&gt;.\nThis quest is completed by speaking with atleast 3 NPCs from Broken Valley Village, who have any information about the location of the Dragon. \nYou can find &lt;a href=\"Ollie\"&gt;Ollie&lt;/a&gt; at the entrance to the &lt;a href=\"Black%20Boar\"&gt;Black Boar&lt;/a&gt; Inn which is a large building built into a cliff on the left side from the gate you entered the village. &lt;a href=\"Romon\"&gt;Romon&lt;/a&gt; can be found near the &lt;a href=\"Chapel\"&gt;Chapel&lt;/a&gt; which can be accessed by going around the Black Boar inn and crossing the small bridge. &lt;a href=\"Winthrop\"&gt;Winthrop&lt;/a&gt; can be found guarding the entrance to the &lt;a href=\"Watermill\"&gt;Watermill&lt;/a&gt; (building in middle of the village), near the training guards. &lt;a href=\"Sean\"&gt;Sean&lt;/a&gt; can be found patrolling the wall above training guards.\nOnce you have spoken with enough NPCs a message will appear on screen indicating that there has been progress in the quest. The quest will also be marked green in the quest log.\nOnce this happens go to &lt;a href=\"Barracks\"&gt;Barracks&lt;/a&gt;, which is a tower connected to the walls protecting the village from the wilderness. Once inside go to the ground floor where you can find Rhode speaking with Lieutenant &lt;a href=\"Louis\"&gt;Louis&lt;/a&gt;.\nSpeak with Rhode and tell her what you have found in order to complete the quest."}
