{"id": "14241", "revid": "43671602", "url": "https://divinity.fandom.com/wiki?curid=14241", "title": "Cheese Bread", "text": "Cheese bread is a &lt;a href=\"Original%20Sin%202%20Consumables\"&gt;consumable item&lt;/a&gt; in \"\".\nCharacteristics.\n is a consumable item which will heal 10 % of maximum Vitality and increase &lt;a href=\"Constitution\"&gt;Constitution&lt;/a&gt; by 1 point when consumed. Characters with &lt;a href=\"Original%20Sin%202%20Talents\"&gt;Five-Star Diner talent&lt;/a&gt; are healed for 20 % maximum Vitality and gain 2 points into Constitution. Effects last 6 turns.\nPoisoned is a food that was poisoned through various means (either &lt;a href=\"Poison%20Bottle%20%28Original%20Sin%202%29\"&gt;poison bottle&lt;/a&gt; or &lt;a href=\"Zaikk%27s%20Talon\"&gt;Zaikk's Talon&lt;/a&gt;). Instead of healing it will deal poison damage equal to 10 % of the consumers maximum Vitality, rendering it unsafe for the living but safe for &lt;a href=\"Undead\"&gt;Undead&lt;/a&gt; and increase &lt;a href=\"Constitution\"&gt;Constitution&lt;/a&gt; by 1 point. The effects last 6 turns.\nLocations.\nTraders.\nFollowing NPCs sell a large variety of food and thus have a solid chance (not guaranteed) of having in their stock. Note that as a consumable item may be very randomly sold by other NPCs."}
