{"id": "2253", "revid": "27868532", "url": "https://divinity.fandom.com/wiki?curid=2253", "title": "Lock and Key", "text": "Lock and Key is a &lt;a href=\"Ego%20Draconis%20quests\"&gt;sub-quest&lt;/a&gt; of the main quest &lt;a href=\"Hall%20of%20Echoes%20Bound\"&gt;Hall of Echoes Bound&lt;/a&gt; in \"\". \nDetailed Walkthrough.\nYou must find the &lt;a href=\"Hall%20of%20Echoes%20Sigil\"&gt;Hall of Echoes Sigil&lt;/a&gt; that will open the door to &lt;a href=\"Hall%20of%20Echoes\"&gt;The Hall of Echoes&lt;/a&gt; by defeating &lt;a href=\"Ba%27al\"&gt;Ba'al&lt;/a&gt; in the &lt;a href=\"Broken%20Valley%20Mine\"&gt;mine&lt;/a&gt;. The mine is located near where the &lt;a href=\"Quarry%20Waypoint%20Shrine\"&gt;Quarry Waypoint Shrine&lt;/a&gt; was prior to the region being poisoned. In order to get in alternate entry must be found.\nTo gain access to the mine, stop at the &lt;a href=\"Broken%20Valley%20Mine%20Tower\"&gt;mine tower&lt;/a&gt; first. Inside the building, there are two level 27 &lt;a href=\"Black%20Ring\"&gt;Black Ring&lt;/a&gt; members. Once defeated go to the top of the tower (there several chests along the way, one of them requires a key which is found on a desk on the top floor). Here &lt;a href=\"Williams\"&gt;Williams&lt;/a&gt; can be found, who of an alternative way to enter the mine and gives &lt;a href=\"the%20Dragon%20Knight\"&gt;the Dragon Knight&lt;/a&gt; the key. At the end of the conversation a mini-quest, &lt;a href=\"A%20Guild%20Without%20a%20Master\"&gt;A Guild Without a Master&lt;/a&gt;, automatically begins.\nOnce outside, get back into &lt;a href=\"Dragon%20Form\"&gt;Dragon Form&lt;/a&gt; and head southeast towards the mine entrance, which is marked on the map; the area is protected by towers.\nAfter entering the mine, either loot it thoroughly while completing the quest, or ignore much of the mine and focus on getting the Hall of Echoes Sigil. Follow the path from the entry until reaching a four-way junction. Note the locked door to the left (north) and continue straight ahead (east). The path soon curves north. Go north to a heavily populated area with level 28 Black Ring members, &lt;a href=\"demons\"&gt;demons&lt;/a&gt; and summoned &lt;a href=\"Skeleton\"&gt;fire skeletons&lt;/a&gt;; an officer named &lt;a href=\"Amon\"&gt;Amon&lt;/a&gt; will attack as well. Once he's dead, loot his key, then turn around and return to the locked door at the junction. Unlock the door and head north to another door (labelled Maxos Door). Once the door is entered it will automatically and permanently close. Inside &lt;a href=\"Ba%27al\"&gt;Ba'al&lt;/a&gt; (level 30) must be faced, who spawns a lot of demon helpers (level 28), some of which are summoners and therefore summon even more.\nDefeat Ba'al and loot the Hall of Echoes Sigil to end the quest. "}
