{"id": "2429", "revid": "94702", "url": "https://divinity.fandom.com/wiki?curid=2429", "title": "Lost Soul", "text": " is a &lt;a href=\"Ego%20Draconis%20quests\"&gt;side quest&lt;/a&gt; accepted from &lt;a href=\"Lovis\"&gt;Lovis&lt;/a&gt; in &lt;a href=\"Lovis%27%20Tower\"&gt;Lovis' Tower&lt;/a&gt;. He asks you to enter &lt;a href=\"Maxos%20Temple\"&gt;Maxos Temple&lt;/a&gt;, complete a series of puzzles, kill \"the dragon\" &lt;a href=\"Amdusias\"&gt;Amdusias&lt;/a&gt; and retrieve his soul.\nDetailed Walkthrough.\nEnter Maxos Temple and complete first three puzzles in order to unlock teleport leading to Eternal Maze puzzle. After completing the final puzzle you must complete the quest &lt;a href=\"Dragon%20No%20More\"&gt;Dragon No More&lt;/a&gt; in order to obtain the Soul Stone.\nReturn to &lt;a href=\"Lovis\"&gt;Lovis&lt;/a&gt; and give him his Soul Stone in order to complete the quest and receive a reward from him."}
{"id": "19450", "revid": "53418829", "url": "https://divinity.fandom.com/wiki?curid=19450", "title": "Lost and Found", "text": " is a &lt;a href=\"Original%20Sin%202%20Quests\"&gt;side quest&lt;/a&gt; in \"\".\nDetailed walkthrough.\nIn order to start the quest you must speak with &lt;a href=\"Lagan\"&gt;Lagan&lt;/a&gt;. To reach him through the &lt;a href=\"Driftwood\"&gt;Driftwood&lt;/a&gt;, pass down the road between the &lt;a href=\"Magister\"&gt;Magister&lt;/a&gt; tent and &lt;a href=\"Driftwood%20Fishworks\"&gt;Driftwood Fishworks&lt;/a&gt;, go across the water and you will find Lagan standing on a wooden ramp near water. Initiating the conversation with any character automatically starts the quest. After that go into the water and pick the &lt;a href=\"Copper%20Ring\"&gt;Copper Ring&lt;/a&gt; which should reveal itself as the Godwoken come near. \nPicking up the ring will immediatelly summon &lt;a href=\"Voidwoken\"&gt;Voidwoken&lt;/a&gt;, namely 1 &lt;a href=\"Voidwoken%20Deep-Dweller\"&gt;Voidwoken Deep-Dweller&lt;/a&gt; (level 10) and 5 &lt;a href=\"Slippery%20Voidling\"&gt;Slippery Voidling&lt;/a&gt;s (level 9) and force Lagan to run away. \nAll of the Voidwoken have high Magic Armour and various immunities including immunity to Stun. Its recommended to attack them with Physical damage or Earth Damage as all Voidwoken have weakness towards it. The Deep-Dweller Voidwoken will have for 1 round due to Wet status - 40% resistance to Air which may be crucial to dispatching it quickly as it increases the resistances of nearby Voidwoken thanks to &lt;a href=\"Leadership\"&gt;Leadership&lt;/a&gt; stat. All Voidwoken leave Cursed Water surface whenever they receive damage. Slippery Voidlings will use the skill &lt;a href=\"Amphibian%20Leap\"&gt;Amphibian Leap&lt;/a&gt; to move jump across obstacles whilst giving them Hasted status. They will attack with the skill &lt;a href=\"Charged%20Phlegm\"&gt;Charged Phlegm&lt;/a&gt; which deals Air damage, their normal attack will deal Air damage and leave their target Cursed. upon death they leave \"Cursed Electrified Steam\" cloud in their place. The Deep-Dweller will use &lt;a href=\"Void%20Glide\"&gt;Void Glide&lt;/a&gt; skill to teleport himself and attack with its claws, dealing large amount of physical damage.\nAfter the Voidwoken are dead Lagan will return back and can be spoken to.\nAfter that you have two options. Tell him you have found the ring or withhold mentioning it. If you withhold mentioning the ring the quest will not be closed. In order to finish it you must mention to Lagan you had found the ring and then decide whether to give him the ring for free or ask for reward. Giving him the ring for free closes the quest, asking for reward force the Godwoken to pass a persuasion (Intelligence, Memory, Finesse and Constitution). Passing the persuasion yields 1 additional Gold. Afterwards you can decide to give him the ring or to keep it.\nIf the &lt;a href=\"Godwoken\"&gt;Godwoken&lt;/a&gt; successfully persuades him to pay for it, he will claim that what he is giving is the last of his dinner money, however his locker in the nearby fishery still has gold in it."}
