{"id": "12137", "revid": "43671602", "url": "https://divinity.fandom.com/wiki?curid=12137", "title": "Love Grenade", "text": "Love grenade is a &lt;a href=\"Munitions%20%28Original%20Sin%202%29%23Grenades\"&gt;grenade&lt;/a&gt; in \"\".\nCharacteristics.\n is a throwable grenade that deals no damage on its own but will inflict &lt;a href=\"Charmed%20%28Status%29\"&gt;Charmed Status&lt;/a&gt; for 2 turns in a 4m radius to all characters if the Magic Armour of affected characters reaches 0 or they do not possess an immunity to this status.\nAll characters can throw this grenade but due to it dealing no damage, its effectiveness cannot be increased. \nSince is a grenade it is affected by &lt;a href=\"Original%20Sin%202%20Talents\"&gt;Ambidextrous&lt;/a&gt; talent which decreases the cost of using grenades and scrolls by 1 AP when the secondary hand is free. is also affected by &lt;a href=\"Original%20Sin%202%20Talents\"&gt;Slingshot&lt;/a&gt; which increases its range by 5 meters and by &lt;a href=\"Original%20Sin%202%20Talents\"&gt;Far Out Man&lt;/a&gt; talent which increases range by 2 meters."}
