{"id": "19464", "revid": "43671602", "url": "https://divinity.fandom.com/wiki?curid=19464", "title": "Mage", "text": "The mage is a character &lt;a href=\"Divine%20Divinity%20classes\"&gt;class&lt;/a&gt; in \"&lt;a href=\"Divine%20Divinity\"&gt;Divine Divinity&lt;/a&gt;\".\nCharacteristics.\nMages are better suited to avoid physical contact, instead they rely on magic. They begin with an increase to &lt;a href=\"Mana\"&gt;Mana&lt;/a&gt; and &lt;a href=\"Intelligence%23Divine%20Divinity\"&gt;Intelligence&lt;/a&gt;.\nMale mages begin with the &lt;a href=\"Summon%20Vermin\"&gt;Summon Vermin&lt;/a&gt; and &lt;a href=\"Meteorstrike\"&gt;Meteorstrike&lt;/a&gt; skills, whereas female mages begin with &lt;a href=\"Meteorstrike\"&gt;Meteorstrike&lt;/a&gt; and &lt;a href=\"Bless%20%28Divine%20Divinity%29\"&gt;Bless&lt;/a&gt;."}
