{"id": "16409", "revid": "43671602", "url": "https://divinity.fandom.com/wiki?curid=16409", "title": "Magic Armour Potion", "text": "The is a &lt;a href=\"Consumables%20%28Original%20Sin%202%29\"&gt;consumable item&lt;/a&gt; in \"\".\nCharacteristics.\nSmall magic armour potion is a potion which increases Physical Armour by 38 points for 5 turns. If character has &lt;a href=\"Original%20Sin%202%20Talents\"&gt;Five-Star Diner talent&lt;/a&gt; the amount of Magic Armour increased will be 76 points instead of 38. Its weight is 0.25 and value is 15 gold.\nMedium magic armour potion is a potion which increases Physical Armour by 134 points for 5 turns. If character has Five-Star Diner talent the amount of Magic Armour increased will be 268 points instead of 134. Its weight is 0.25 and value is 55 gold.\nLarge magic armour potion is a potion which increases Physical Armour by 321 points for 5 turns. If character has Five-Star Diner talent the amount of Magic Armour increased will be 642 points instead of 321. Its weight is 0.25 and value is 95 gold.\nGiant magic armour potion is a potion which increases Physical Armour by 625 points for 5 turns. If character has Five-Star Diner talent the amount of Magic Armour increased will be 1250 points instead of 625. Its weight is 0.25 and value is 170 gold.\nLocations.\nTraders.\nFollowing NPCs sell a large variety of potions and thus have a solid chance (not guaranteed) of having in their stock. Note that as a consumable item may be very randomly sold by other NPCs."}
{"id": "15225", "revid": "43671602", "url": "https://divinity.fandom.com/wiki?curid=15225", "title": "Magic Barrier", "text": " is a &lt;a href=\"Divine%20Divinity%20skills%23Way%20of%20the%20survivor\"&gt;Survivor skill&lt;/a&gt; in \"&lt;a href=\"Divine%20Divinity\"&gt;Divine Divinity&lt;/a&gt;\".\nDescription.\nThis passive skill when learnt by &lt;a href=\"Lucian\"&gt;Lucian&lt;/a&gt;, increases all of his resistances by 5 points. The skill is passive and cummulative and each point invested adds futher 5 points into resistances. At maximum rank the skill offers + 25 resistance towards fire, poison, lightning and spiritual damage. "}
