{"id": "14770", "revid": "46132361", "url": "https://divinity.fandom.com/wiki?curid=14770", "title": "Magic Mirror", "text": " is a &lt;a href=\"Divine%20Divinity%20quest%20items\"&gt;quest item&lt;/a&gt; in \"&lt;a href=\"Divine%20Divinity\"&gt;Divine Divinity&lt;/a&gt;\"\nCharacteristics.\nA single use mirror with magical properties, they are very common, however, fakes are very common. When dropped into a pool of water, they can be used to duplicate an item.\nLocations.\nThe magic mirror can be found in the vacant house in the northern part of &lt;a href=\"Aleroth\"&gt;Aleroth&lt;/a&gt;, sat on a large package."}
{"id": "3583", "revid": "49135869", "url": "https://divinity.fandom.com/wiki?curid=3583", "title": "Magic Missile", "text": "Magic Missile is a &lt;a href=\"Dragon%20Knight%20Saga%20Skills%23Mage\"&gt;Mage skill&lt;/a&gt; that can be used by &lt;a href=\"the%20Dragon%20Knight\"&gt;the Dragon Knight&lt;/a&gt; in \"\".\nDescription.\nMagic Missile is a active Mage skill that allows the Knight to hurl several magic missiles at enemies. This skill can be cast with any weapon in hand. \nThe magic damage of your weapons increases the damage of this skill. Meaning dual-wielding two weapons with high magic damage maximalizes the damage output of magic missiles (the dual-wield skill does not matter). "}
