{"id": "19209", "revid": "49426621", "url": "https://divinity.fandom.com/wiki?curid=19209", "title": "Magic Potion", "text": "The magic potions are &lt;a href=\"Divine%20Divinity%20consumables\"&gt;potions&lt;/a&gt; in \"&lt;a href=\"Divine%20Divinity\"&gt;Divine Divinity&lt;/a&gt;\".\nCharacteristics.\nBlue coloured potions, which restore fixed amounts of magic when consumed.\nThey can be made by combining &lt;a href=\"Empty%20Flask%20%28Divine%20Divinity%29\"&gt;Empty Flasks&lt;/a&gt; with Blue Mushrooms or Blue Herbs, and increased in size with &lt;a href=\"Augmentor\"&gt;Augmentor&lt;/a&gt;. They also can be combined with &lt;a href=\"Health%20Potion\"&gt;Health Potions&lt;/a&gt; to create &lt;a href=\"Restoration%20Potion\"&gt;Restoration Potions&lt;/a&gt;, or with &lt;a href=\"Stamina%20Potion\"&gt;Stamina Potions&lt;/a&gt; to create &lt;a href=\"Shadows%20Potion\"&gt;Shadows Potions&lt;/a&gt;.\nLocations.\nOften found as random loot."}
