{"id": "19514", "revid": "43671602", "url": "https://divinity.fandom.com/wiki?curid=19514", "title": "Mana", "text": "Mana is a core attribute that determines a character's magical energy storage. A portion of mana is used with all non-passive skills. \n\"Divine Divinity\".\nIntelligence affects only Mana. It can be increased from &lt;a href=\"Charms%20%28Divine%20Divinity%29%23Intelligence\"&gt;Charms&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a href=\"Bless%20%28Divine%20Divinity%29\"&gt;Bless&lt;/a&gt;, and various Prefixes and Suffixes from gear."}
{"id": "3625", "revid": "43671602", "url": "https://divinity.fandom.com/wiki?curid=3625", "title": "Mana Efficiency", "text": "Mana Efficiency is a &lt;a href=\"Dragon%20Knight%20Saga%20Skills%23Mage\"&gt;Mage skill&lt;/a&gt; that can be used by &lt;a href=\"the%20Dragon%20Knight\"&gt;the Dragon Knight&lt;/a&gt; in \"\".\nDescription.\nMana Efficiency is a passive Mage skill that lowers the cost of mana needed to cast spells and skills. Due to its nature, once learnt, it will be always active.\nNote: The last level of this skill is only available to characters level 48 and above; very few players will reach this level by the game's end."}
{"id": "3635", "revid": "43671602", "url": "https://divinity.fandom.com/wiki?curid=3635", "title": "Mana Leech", "text": "Mana Leech is a &lt;a href=\"Dragon%20Knight%20Saga%20Skills%23Mage\"&gt;Mage skill&lt;/a&gt; that can be used by &lt;a href=\"the%20Dragon%20Knight\"&gt;the Dragon Knight&lt;/a&gt; in \"\".\nDescription.\nMana Leech is a passive Mage skill that allows the Knight to steal mana from their enemies as they wound them. Due to its nature, once learnt, it will be always active."}
