{"id": "15134", "revid": "31775388", "url": "https://divinity.fandom.com/wiki?curid=15134", "title": "Maria", "text": " is a &lt;a href=\"Divine%20Divinity%20characters\"&gt;human&lt;/a&gt; in 1218 AD.\nBackground.\nShe lived in wealthy family, until Merchants guild actions caused her family to lose reputation and wealth.\nHer father did business with elves, and one day guild demanded third of his profits. He refused, calling the guild secretary greedy fool. This caused guild to have her father arrested due to breaking regulation law.\nSince then, she has been longing for revenge to this secretary. She does know many dirty and intimate secrets of many guild members, which guild would like to keep buried."}
