{"id": "12870", "revid": "43671602", "url": "https://divinity.fandom.com/wiki?curid=12870", "title": "Mashed Potatoes", "text": "The ' is a &lt;a href=\"Consumables%20%28Original%20Sin%202%29\"&gt;consumable item&lt;/a&gt; in ' and \"\".\nCharacteristics.\n is a consumable item which will heal 10 % of maximum Vitality and grant + 1 point to &lt;a href=\"Strength\"&gt;Strength&lt;/a&gt; upon consuming. If character has &lt;a href=\"Original%20Sin%202%20Talents\"&gt;Five-Star Diner talent&lt;/a&gt; it will heal 20 % of maximum Vitality and grant + 2 points to &lt;a href=\"Strength\"&gt;Strength&lt;/a&gt;. The effect of last 6 turns.\nPoisoned is a consumable item that was poisoned through various means (either &lt;a href=\"Poison%20Bottle%20%28Original%20Sin%202%29\"&gt;poison bottle&lt;/a&gt; or &lt;a href=\"Zaikk%27s%20Talon\"&gt;Zaikk's Talon&lt;/a&gt;). Poisoning the will reduce its value to 0. Instead of healing it will deal poison damage equal to 10 % of the consumers maximum Vitality, rendering it unsafe for the living but safe for &lt;a href=\"Undead\"&gt;Undead&lt;/a&gt; and grant + 1 points to &lt;a href=\"Strength\"&gt;Strength&lt;/a&gt;. \nIf character has &lt;a href=\"Original%20Sin%202%20Talents\"&gt;Five-Star Diner talent&lt;/a&gt; the will deal poison damage equal to 20 % of the consumers maximum Vitality and grant + 2 points to &lt;a href=\"Strength\"&gt;Strength&lt;/a&gt;. The effects last 6 turns. \nLocations.\nTraders.\nFollowing NPCs sell a large variety of food and thus have a solid chance (not guaranteed) of having in their stock. Note that as a consumable item may be very randomly sold by other NPCs."}
