{"id": "14373", "revid": "43671602", "url": "https://divinity.fandom.com/wiki?curid=14373", "title": "Hannag", "text": "Hannag is a &lt;a href=\"sourcerer\"&gt;sourcerer&lt;/a&gt; hiding in a ruins of &lt;a href=\"the%20Temple%20of%20Rhalic\"&gt;the Temple of Rhalic&lt;/a&gt; on &lt;a href=\"Reaper%27s%20Coast\"&gt;Reaper's Coast&lt;/a&gt; in 1242 AD.\nBackground.\nHannag is a master sourcerer and expert in portals and magical devices. During the Chaos War when &lt;a href=\"Divine%20Order\"&gt;Divine Order&lt;/a&gt; was being outnumbered by the &lt;a href=\"Black%20Ring\"&gt;Black Ring&lt;/a&gt; forces, approaching the elven lands, she was on the advice of the &lt;a href=\"House%20of%20War\"&gt;House of War&lt;/a&gt; emmissaries approached by &lt;a href=\"Lucian\"&gt;Lucian&lt;/a&gt; and &lt;a href=\"Alexandar\"&gt;Alexandar&lt;/a&gt; and told to make a Deathfog bomb, with the instructions provided by &lt;a href=\"Farzanah\"&gt;Farzanah&lt;/a&gt;.\u00a0\nYears later in 1242 AD, she had been in contact with &lt;a href=\"Dwarves\"&gt;dwarven&lt;/a&gt; scientist &lt;a href=\"Zanisima\"&gt;Zanisima&lt;/a&gt; who recovered the old device and tried to recreate the Deathfog bomb but the device was damaged and needed Hannag's expertise to \"repair and atune\" It is unknown how the device got damaged to begin with, or if she would actually help, but a third communique found next to Zanisima's device indicated that Hannag has no interest of doing so and that she has ignored the previous requests at fixing the device. \nDuring this time she started teaching a young sourcerer &lt;a href=\"Gwydian%20Rince\"&gt;Gwydian Rince&lt;/a&gt;. She has been found by magisters in &lt;a href=\"Paradise%20Downs\"&gt;Paradise Downs&lt;/a&gt;. While defending herself from magisters a &lt;a href=\"Voidwoken%20Harbinger\"&gt;Voidwoken Harbinger&lt;/a&gt; was summoned and ravaged the entire area, killing magisters in the process. Fleeing to &lt;a href=\"Cloisterwood\"&gt;Cloisterwood&lt;/a&gt; she got surrounded by magisters in the ruins of the Temple of Rhalic."}
