{"id": "14925", "revid": "27868532", "url": "https://divinity.fandom.com/wiki?curid=14925", "title": "Harriet", "text": " is a &lt;a href=\"Divine%20Divinity%20characters\"&gt;character&lt;/a&gt; in \"&lt;a href=\"Divine%20Divinity\"&gt;Divine Divinity&lt;/a&gt;\".\nBackground.\nHarriet is staying at The Blue Boar Inn and wishes to leave as soon as possible. She lived in a cottage with her family before the orcs pillaged the village they were living in. Before leaving for her relatives, she wants her uncle in &lt;a href=\"Verdistis\"&gt;Verdistis&lt;/a&gt; to be informed about her fate. However, during the course of her stay at the inn, she takes a cleaning job from &lt;a href=\"Splinter\"&gt;Splinter&lt;/a&gt; and remains at the inn rather than traveling onwards as originally intended.\nInteractions with the Player Character.\nShe wants &lt;a href=\"Lucian\"&gt;Lucian&lt;/a&gt; to deliver a &lt;a href=\"letter%20to%20Afrasam\"&gt;letter to Afrasam&lt;/a&gt;, who is the innkeeper of the &lt;a href=\"Ducal%20Inn\"&gt;Ducal Inn&lt;/a&gt; in &lt;a href=\"Verdistis\"&gt;Verdistis&lt;/a&gt;."}
